stimulus:

3. Next, you will see a series of test pictures from the list you just studied. For each picture, press the "J" key if you recognize it as one you have seen in the current list. Press the "F" key if you don’t recognize it as one from the current list.

You will begin with a practice list, followed by nine formal test lists. For each test, respond based only on the list you JUST studied. If a picture appeared in a previous list but not the current one, press the "F" key.

Do not worry if you are unsure about some test pictures. This is normal, but please make your best guess.

Press the "Enter" key to start the practice list.

Accumulated accuracy will be displayed throughout the experiment. Please pay attention and try to get an averaged performance higher than 60% (chance level is 50%).


You will begin with a practice list, followed by nine formal test lists. For each test, respond based only on the list you JUST studied. If a picture appeared in a previous list but not the current one, press the "F" key.

Do not worry if you are unsure about some test pictures. This is normal, but please make your best guess.

Press the "Enter" key to start the practice list.

Press the "Enter" key to start the practice list.

stimulus:
1. A list of 30 pictures will appear on the screen one at a time. Study the pictures as they appear.

2. After a brief blank period, you will see a series of numbers. Add these numbers as they appear. When prompted with "TYPE THE SUM," use the number keys to enter your answer.

3. Next, you will see a series of test pictures from the list you just studied. For each picture, press the "J" key if you recognize it as one you have seen in the current list. Press the "F" key if you don’t recognize it as one from the current list.
Accumulated accuracy will be displayed throughout the experiment. Please pay attention and try to get an averaged performance higher than 60% (chance level is 50%).


You will begin with a practice list, followed by nine formal test lists. For each test, respond based only on the list you JUST studied. If a picture appeared in a previous list but not the current one, press the "F" key.

Do not worry if you are unsure about some test pictures. This is normal, but please make your best guess.

Press the "Enter" key to start the practice list.
